## Project Nature

{{PROJECT_NAME}} is an FXL spoke application — a standalone system that connects
to the FXL Core hub via the FXL contract API. It follows FXL SDK standards
for code quality, security, and structure.

- **App ID:** {{PROJECT_SLUG}}
- **Contract Version:** 1.0 (read-only)
- **Hub Connection:** FXL Core consumes this app's data via `/api/fxl/*` endpoints

