## Architecture Rule

**The React frontend NEVER calls Supabase directly.**
All data access goes through the Hono backend.

```
Browser (React) → Hono Backend → Supabase
```

- Frontend communicates with backend via `frontend/src/lib/api-client.ts`
- Backend holds `SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY` — never exposed to the browser
- Shared types live in `shared/types/` — imported by both frontend and backend

