## Security Rules

- ALL secrets in `.env.local` (NEVER committed)
- Frontend vars prefixed with `VITE_` only
- `SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY` is backend-only — NEVER prefix with `VITE_`
- Clerk JWT validated by backend `auth.ts` middleware on every authenticated request
- `org_id` extracted from server-validated JWT (never from client)
- RLS enabled on EVERY Supabase table
- Every table has `org_id text NOT NULL` column
- Security headers set in `frontend/vercel.json`

