## FXL Contract

FXL contract endpoints live in `backend/src/routes/fxl/` (NOT in frontend).
They are protected by `fxl-api-key.ts` middleware for data endpoints.
`/api/fxl/manifest` and `/api/fxl/health` are public.

| Endpoint | Description |
|----------|-------------|
| GET /api/fxl/manifest | App metadata, entities, widgets (public) |
| GET /api/fxl/entities/:type | Paginated entity list (API key required) |
| GET /api/fxl/entities/:type/:id | Single entity (API key required) |
| GET /api/fxl/widgets/:id/data | Widget data (API key required) |
| GET /api/fxl/search?q= | Cross-entity search (API key required) |
| GET /api/fxl/health | Health + contract version (public) |

Contract is v1 (read-only). All entity endpoints filter by `org_id`.

