## What NEVER to Do

- Never use `any` in TypeScript
- Never commit `.env.local`
- Never call Supabase from the React frontend
- Never prefix `SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY` with `VITE_`
- Never create tables without RLS
- Never trust client-provided org_id
- Never add dependencies without documenting here
- Never skip the quality gates above
